6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both InVideo AI and Visla share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Video, Auto Captions, Templates, Stock Footage. On the other hand, Visla uniquely offers Screen Recording, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, InVideo AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Visla scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Visla comes in at a lower starting price of $24/mo, while InVideo AI begins at $25/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. InVideo AI's free tier and Visla's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
